 or video click on the icon in the top-right corner and youll see two options.";i:10;s:30:"Choose Photo and Choose Video.";i:11;s:103:"In the drop-down menu select the file type you want to save your image as and then choose a resolution.";i:12;s:62:"Click Download when youre ready to save your background image.";i:13;s:66:"After your image downloads you can use it as your Zoom background.";i:14;s:40:"How to Use a Custom Background in Gmail.";i:15;s:79:"To use a custom virtual background scroll over to the right and tap the button.";i:16;s:74:"Zoom will open a file manager and you can select any image on your device.";i:17;s:52:"Zoom for Android does not support video backgrounds.";i:18;s:59:"Once you select an image it will appear as your background.";i:19;s:51:"Tap Close to leave the background picker interface.";i:20;s:105:"Download a virtual Zoom background to display an image or video as your background during a Zoom Meeting.";i:21;s:227:"Office background room wall beach hd background nature google meet background home window blur living room free background abstract texture dark background zoom background landscape city library sky technology interior skyline.";i:22;s:21:"Start a Zoom meeting.";i:23;s:127:"At the bottom left corner of the window find the up arrow next to the video icon click it then click Choose Virtual Background.";i:24;s:32:"Click Choose Virtual Background.";i:25;s:72:"Find the plus icon on the right hand side click it then click Add Video.";i:26;s:144:"To do so enable the I have a green screen setting in the bottom-left of the Virtual Backgrounds sub-tab of the Backgrounds Filters settings tab.";i:27;s:121:"When you enable the setting Zoom will attempt to detect your background colour and automatically start filtering with it.";i:28;s:52:"If the detected background colour isnt working well.";i:29;s:97:"Locate the file on your device and select it to instantly see your new background inside of Zoom.";i:30;s:55:"The Virtual Background screen inside of Zooms settings.";i:31;s:90:"After you upload the custom virtual background you can use it in any subsequent Zoom call.";i:32;s:149:"To access your virtual backgrounds while inside of a Zoom call click the small arrow next to to the Stop Video button and then select Choose Virtual.";i:33;s:90:"In the Settings window click on the Virtual Background tab on the left side of the window.";i:34;s:90:"To set a video background in Zoom click on a thumbnail marked with a icon see image below.";i:35;s:67:"Zoom provides a couple of videos itself in the app but you can add.";i:36;s:135:"Click Choose Virtual Background Now you can pick one of the 2 video background that Zoom provides you or you can upload your own video.";i:37;s:115:"Most meteorologists use a green screen to project the weather behind them while they narrate the upcoming forecast.";i:38;s:99:"You can use the same type of green screen in Zoom meetings to create an illusion in the background.";i:39;s:85:"In this case a green screen works hand-in-hand with Zooms Virtual Background feature.";i:40;s:105:"The Zoom Virtual Background Maker by Kapwing quickly scales a picture to the perfect dimensions for Zoom.";i:41;s:75:"Click the blue make it button below to open the template in Kapwing Studio.";i:42;s:132:"From here click replace to upload an image from your device paste an image URL or click image search to browse pictures from Google.";i:43;s:86:"Here is a list of steps on how to make the blurred background in Zoom meetings on Mac.";i:44;s:90:"Open the updated Zoom and choose the Settings button which is located under the user name.";i:45;s:75:"Now choose the Background Filters button from the left side of the toolbar.";i:46;s:49:"Start by logging inopening Zoom on your computer.";i:47;s:48:"The upper right corner you will see a gear icon.";i:48;s:37:"Click the gear to open the main menu.";i:49;s:56:"On the left-hand side all of the categories will appear.";i:50;s:37:"Select the Background Filters option.";i:51;s:57:"For Zoom mobile app iOS only Android is no available yet.";i:52;s:31:"Sign in to the Zoom mobile app.";i:53;s:49:"While in a Zoom meeting tap More in the controls.";i:54;s:28:"Then tap Virtual Background.";i:55;s:72:"Tap the background you would like to apply or tap to upload a new image.";i:56;s:45:"The background will be automatically applied.";i:57;s:140:"To add it to Zoom click the gear icon on the upper right-hand side of the main screen of the desktop Zoom app and select Virtual Background.";i:58;s:43:"For Zooms virtual background video to work.";}}